roared up the steep freeway grade north of Black Canyon City. For
many people, a conversion van is the vehicle of choice for
long-distance traveling. Not quite as commodious as the Starship
Enterprise, there's plenty of room in terms of modern-day
earthbound vehicles, plus a kid-pleasing video system for movies or
video-games. By BOB GOLFEN.
