sales representatives have created two aisles stocked mostly with
Pepsi soft drinks and Frito-Lay snack food. It is part of the
company's marketing strategy known as the Power of One, a New
Age-sounding slogan for selling soda and snack food together and
maybe Pepsi's other core product, fruit juice, too. By Constance L.
