</P>
<P>
   The society recently held its monthly meeting at the Sylmar home
of 83-year-old Frank Inn, who gained fame in Hollywood as an animal
trainer for teaching Benji tricks and for animals that have
appeared on the television shows ``The Beverly Hillbillies,''
``Green Acres'' and ``The Addams Family.''
