 &HT;    1ST LEDE
 &HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    Eds: Updates SHOOT budget.
 &HT;    
 &HT;    The Cox News Service spot news budget for Sunday, Aug. 1, 1999.
 &HT;    c.1999 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
