<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-GRAPHICS-FILES-NYT </SLUG>
  
<TEXT>
<P>
   Here is a listing of the New York Times News Service Macintosh
graphics files that moved Saturday, 07/31/99. Included is the
corresponding story slug and the size. All graphics have been
posted on PressLink, NewsCom and the Wieck Photo Database.
</P>
<P>
   JAPAN_Akashima locator -- 1 x 1 3/4 -- JAPAN-DECLINE
</P>
<P>
   JAPAN_Aging population -- 2 x 4 1/8 -- JAPAN-DECLINE
</P>
<P>
   CONGO_Goma locator -- 1 x 2 1/8 -- CONGO-PEACE
</P>
<P>
   RUSSIA_Birobidzhan locator -- 1 x 2 3/4 -- RUSSIA-PRIVATE-FARMS
</P>
<P>
   KOSOVO_Gornje Obrinje locator -- 1 x 2 1/2 -- KOSOVO-REBUILD
</P>
<P>
   MIAMI_Expressway map -- 1 x 3 5/8 -- MIAMI-TRAFFIC
</P>
<P>
   NANTUCKET_Locator map -- 1 x 2 1/8 -- NANTUCKET-DEVELOP
</P>
